author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
When should you bring in a collaborator vs. go it alone on a project? At which special effects company would Adam Savage want to work if he went back to modelmaking? In this live stream, Adam answers these questions from Tested members Gwen Protheroe and Patrick Hennessy, whom we thank for their support. Join this channel to support Tested and get access to perks, like asking Adam a question:

04:06 Worst-case career scenario
09:58 Adam's phone interrupts
